@startuml
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid

actor "Quản trị viên" as User #Yellow
boundary "RegistrationsPage" as UI #Yellow
boundary "AxiosClient" as API #Yellow
control "JwtMiddleware" as MW #Yellow
control "BookingsController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "BookingService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "Booking" as BEnt #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #Yellow

User -> UI : 1: Nhấn nút hành động\ntrên một booking
activate UI

note right of UI : Các hành động có sẵn:\n- Approve (Pending -> Confirmed)\n- Reject (Pending -> Cancelled)\n- Confirm (Approved -> Confirmed)\n- Mark Complete (Confirmed -> Completed)\n- No Show (Confirmed -> Cancelled)

UI -> UI : 1.1: Xác định status enum value:\nConfirmed=1, InProgress=2, Completed=3,\nCancelled=4, Refunded=5
UI -> API : 1.2: PUT /api/Bookings/{id}/status\nHeader: Authorization: Bearer {token}\nBody: {statusNumber}
activate API

API -> API : 1.3: Axios interceptor: gắn Bearer token
API -> MW : 1.4: Request qua JwtMiddleware
activate MW
MW -> MW : 1.5: ValidateToken
alt 1.6: [Token không hợp lệ]
MW --> API : 1.6.1: 401
API --> UI : 1.6.2: Redirect login
else 1.7: [Token hợp lệ]
MW -> MW : 1.7.1: Parse userId từ claim
MW --> Ctrl : 1.7.2: Chuyển tiếp
deactivate MW

activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Ctrl : 1.8: Parse userId từ\nClaimTypes.NameIdentifier
Ctrl -> Ctrl : 1.9: Bind body -> BookingStatus enum
Ctrl -> Svc : 1.10: UpdateStatusAsync(id, status, userId)
activate Svc

Svc -> DB : 1.11: Bookings.GetByIdAsync(id)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.11.1: Booking hoặc null
deactivate DB

alt 1.12: [Booking không tồn tại]
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.12.1: ApiResponse.Fail(\n"Booking not found", 404)
Ctrl --> API : 1.12.2: StatusCode(404)
API --> UI : 1.12.3: Lỗi
UI --> User : 1.12.4: "Booking not found"
else 1.13: [Booking tồn tại]
Svc -> Svc : 1.13.1: booking.Status = status\nbooking.UpdatedBy = userId\nbooking.UpdatedAt = UtcNow

Svc -> DB : 1.13.2: Bookings.UpdateAsync(booking)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : OK
deactivate DB
Svc -> DB : 1.13.3: SaveChangesAsync()
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.13.3.1: OK
deactivate DB

Svc -> DB : 1.13.4: GetByIdAsync(booking.Id)\n(có Customer, Tour,\nBookingDetails, Payments)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.13.4.1: Booking đã cập nhật
deactivate DB
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.13.5: ApiResponse.Ok(result.Data!,\n"Booking status updated")
end

deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> API : 1.14: StatusCode(200)
deactivate Ctrl
API --> UI : 1.15: Response JSON
deactivate API

UI -> UI : 1.16: TanStack Query:\ninvalidateQueries(['registrations'])
UI -> UI : 1.17: Cập nhật trạng thái trong UI
UI --> User : 1.18: Hiển thị trạng thái mới\n(ví dụ: Pending -> Confirmed)
deactivate UI

@enduml
